<h3>Link integrity</h3>
<p>plone.api.content.delete now support the parameter <span>check_linkintegrity. This raises an exception if deleting the object(s) would result in broken links.</span></p>
<h3>kwargs for plone.api.content.transition</h3>
<p><span>plone.api.content.transition now accepts kwargs that can be supplied to the workflow transition.</span></p>
<pre>from plone import api
portal = api.portal.get()
api.content.transition(obj=portal['about'], transition='reject', comment='You had a typo on your page.')
</pre>
<h3>Tuple support in content.find for <span>object_provides</span></h3>
<p>The <span>object_provides parameter allows a tuple of interfaces, as well as a list.</span></p>
